========================================
    ASPEN ~~VERSION~~ [~~DATE~~]
========================================

This is Aspen, a highly extensible web server for Python-based publication,
application, and hybrid websites. You will find documentation in the doc/
directory of this distribution, inline in the source files, and online at:

  http://www.zetadev.com/software/aspen/


